entry.title: NOAA-EDAB/Rpath
entry.summary:
R implementation of the mass balance model Ecopath with Ecosim

Rpath

This is the repository for Rpath - the R implementation of the mass balance algorithms.

The new public facing repository (NOAA-EDAB/Rpath) was established for release with the Rpath manuscript Lucey et al. 2020. The previous repository is no longer maintained.

Rpath was developed and is maintained through a collaboration between the Alaska Fisheries Science Center and the Northeast Fisheries Science Center.

To view release notes please visit the wiki.
